Third-party notices and attributions
================================================================================

NanoMsgSharp is an independent, clean-room reimplementation of the Scalability
Protocols (SP) wire protocol for the .NET platform. It does not include or
derive from the source code of the projects below; it interoperates with them
by implementing the same publicly documented wire protocol.

